        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "This should depend on whether we want to make it optional. If it's mandatory, it's appropriate as the first argument, whereas if it's optional, it's better as the last argument. If we make it optional, we could set the default value to 0 (representing \"current\"), which would be quite handy.",
