        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Consistency is very important here, because there are so many different \"position\" conventions. buf as arg1 is intentional. If we try to be clever then surprises happen and it's painful.\r\n\r\nThe goal of the postion/range abstraction is to clarify the story around positions, so the number 1 priority is to avoid surprises.",
            "created_at": "2026-04-26T10:29:56Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/39414#issuecomment-4321822498",
            "id": 4321822498,
